%% Simurtools Toolbox% Simurtools(TM) is a Matlab Toolbox to % assist in the development of ambulatory human motion systems,. %% This is a product of the SiMuR Lab, at the University of Oviedo. % It is for internal use only, use it at your own risk.%%% Load data files% Read files as generated from different sensor devices:  Xsens(c), Shimmer (c), Optitrack (c)%%%% * <cargar_datos_shimmer.html cargar_datos_shimmer: leer un archivo de datos de los shimmer> % * <cargar_datos_xsens.html cargar_datos_xsens: leer un archivo de datos de los xsens>% * <cargar_datos_silop.html cargar_datos_silop: leer un archivo de datos del proyecto SiLoP> %% IMU calibration% Different methods for obtaining the calibration matrix for reorienting% the initial position of an IMU.%%%% * <calibra_mounting.html calibra_mounting: rotational method based on accelerometers, magnetic and triad.>% * <calibra_anatomical.html calibra_anatomical: calibration based on accelerometers for vertical axis.>% * calibra_ejez: DEPRECATED. Use calibra_mounting instead. %% Estimate distance from acceleration signals % Double integral variations to integrate an acceleration and obtain a displacement.%%%%% * <dinteg_cms.html dinteg_cms: direct doble cumsum method (CMS method)> % * <dinteg_lri.html dinteg_lri: lineal resetting mechanism (LRI method)>% * <dinteg_msi.html dinteg_msi: an integration with mean subtraction (MSI method)> % * <dinteg_ofi.html dinteg_ofi: the optimally filtered integration (OFI method)>% * <dinteg_ddi.html dinteg_ddi: de-drifted integration (DDI method)>% * doble_cumsum_zijlstra: integration with Zijsltra method%%% Attitude Estimation from acc, gyro or magnetic signals% 3D orientation can be estimated from complete IMU signals, such as kalman% filters.%%%% * triad: estimation of 3D orientation by means of accelerometers and gyroscopes% * <orientacioncompas.html orientacioncompas: 2D estimation of the orientation by means of the compass>% * orientaciongiroscopo: 2D estimation by direct integration of the gyroscope% * orientacionkalman: 2D estimation using a kalman filter (gyroscope+magnetic)%%% Gait Events Detection % Different functions related to step events.% %%%% * <eventosRT.html eventosRT: detection of step events sequentially or in real time>% * eventosCOGrecto: Canonical step event detection, normal walking in a straight line %% Step length estimation% Alternatives to estimate the step length.%%%% * distancia_arco: estimation of the pitch length using the arc model% * distancia_pendulo: estimation of the length of the step by means of an inverted pendulum% * distancia_penduloparcial: estimation of step length by means of pendulum+displacement model% * distancia_raizcuarta: estimation of the step length by means of the acceleration amplitude%% Rigid Body 3D Representation% Funtions to draw an object or a frame in 3D: %%% % * <voxel.html voxel: draw a rectangular box>% * <psolido.html psolido: define a prisma defined by corners>% * <pframe.html pframe: draw a frame xyz>%% Special DSP tools% Tools to help in some specific tasks of DSP. They are an addition to the DSP Toolbox of matlab.%%%% * <buscamaximos.html buscamaximos: seeks all the maxims of a signal>% * <buscamaximosth.html buscamaximosth: search for all maxima that exceed a threshold>% * cumcamsimp: numerical integration of cavalieri-simpson% * datacrop: interactive tool to cut a signal